('6870fd47-8a03-5a75-9ce7-51de9c688909', '281b9951-5347-46d1-952b-381fcc811ce8', 'The doctor carefully cleaned the ___ to prevent any infection from spreading.', '醫生仔細地清理傷口，以防止感染擴散。', 'wound', 'bruise', 'fever', 'cough', 'wound 為不規則單字，名詞指「傷口」，動詞指「傷害」。', 'wound 聽起來像 woe (悲哀) → 受了傷 (wound) 當然會感到悲哀 (woe)。', '2026-07-18 17:19:54', '2026-07-18 17:19:54');
